Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H2E3EB0&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidnap the Psychic Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we've invited the famous psychic girl\NKawamura Keiko and her mother to the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx140\fscy150\bord5.5\4a&HFF&\1c&H2B43A9&\pos(320,38)}Shocking Hour
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx160\fscy200\bord1\4c&HFFFFFF&\1c&H985C28&\pos(283.73,380)}Wondrous {\1c&H2B43A9&}ESP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiko is the daughter of\Nparapsychologist Dr. Kawamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll show us her mystical powers, from seeing inside\Nthis box to bending hard spoons with telekinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, our audience already know the answer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiko, can you tell us what's inside this box?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A panda teddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the studio audience and folks\Nwatching at home must be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, she'll bend this spoon with her telekinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She says she can't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You see... Someone in this studio is\Ngenerating negative thought waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's generating negative thought waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She really bent it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alrighty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how you do it! I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Twist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward and back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Twist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sekiguchi Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Beastman Chimera, prepare for orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, GOD Supreme Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawamura Keiko's father, Dr. Kawamura,\Nis the world's leading ESP researcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold Keiko hostage, and force Dr. Kawamura\Ninto assisting our own ESP development.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The chimera is a creature from Greek mythology.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This terrible monster had the heads of a lion and\Ngoat, the tail of a dragon, and could breathe fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My gosh, look at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Experimenting with telekinesis, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kawamura Keiko and Sekiguchi Jun's\Ntelekinesis is something special!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, you're as good as they say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? It's amazing, a human having such an ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it ever fell into the wrong hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful that GOD don't set their sights on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, of course! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiko, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever of?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the chauffeur from the television\Nstation. You mustn't be so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared, little lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. She's just tired from appearing\Non television. Please don't mind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's a psychic for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the car, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my wife and child?\NWhat's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, we're holding them hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Darling!\N-Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Akiko! Keiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Papa, help us!\N-Darling! Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see? Our organisation is so\Npowerful it has its own TV channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you won't cooperate with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, think it over all you need. Just have\Nan answer ready by noon tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist! I knew you were behind this.\NWhat do you want with Dr. Kawamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What indeed? Maybe you\Nshould ask the guy behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One of GOD's wretched monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke! Prepare to be\Nexecuted by the beastman Chimera!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let me finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Try my 10,000 degree flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, let me try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Open... Open, open...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chimera!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When did they--?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dealing with a psychic!\NHow could you leave them unguarded!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them back to their cell and post a guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As Chief of GOD's Secret Police,\NI can't forgive this failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll execute you here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I killed GOD's archenemy, the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't execute me for something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed the X Rider...?\NI'll believe it when I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that Keisuke up to at training time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The youth of today...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Jin Keisuke shown up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm still waiting for--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Chimera wasn't lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you, by the way?\NAn acquaintance of Keisuke's?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you could say we're acquainted...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, until next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What the--? How rude...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief! Chief...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing up--?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted them to think I was dead,\Nbut I might've overdone it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's just a few scratches.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, I need you\Nto do something for me, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can sense some bad guys\Nright outside the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't pick the lock with them there\Nlike I did before! Now we'll never get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, think it over all you need. Just have\Nan answer ready by noon tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Chimera of GOD! The time\Nhas come, give me your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are Akiko and Keiko safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let them go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...If you do, I'll do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! We've got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! I see he got your lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, looks like they're headed for his lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,His lab...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18\i1}Kawamura Parapsychology Labs{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we doing at my lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it's darkest at the foot of the lighthouse.\NYour wife and daughter were under here all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, I'll head in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Darling!\N-You're alright!\N-Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The emotional reunion can wait.\NFirst, you must prove your loyalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our rules demand that you\Nundergo cyborg surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Cyborg surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring all three of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Spare us!\N-Papa, I'm scared!\N-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,At least spare my wife and daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Settle down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Darling!\N-Please!\N-Papa, Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming. He'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiko? Who's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but I can feel someone\Nreally strong getting nearer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way, Keiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Keiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be dropping in any minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, get in already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Long Pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that? Come at me if\Nyou want to get burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't survive that heat\Nunless I cool my body...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too late! Accursed X Rider...\NYou're one tough guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:23:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The psychic girl and her\Nparents have been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what GOD tries next,\Ndon't give up, Kamen Rider X, X, X!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The mysterious prophet Godradamus\Nforetells Tokyo's destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.30,0:23:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as he predicts, GOD's killer\Nsmog throws the city into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But has Rider X uncovered\NGodradamus' true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Godradamus' Great Prophecy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
